[03/06/2019 00:46:45] <font color="#ffffff">-No.</font>
[03/06/2019 00:46:46] <font color="#ffffff">-Almudena.</font>
[03/06/2019 00:46:46] <font color="#ffffff">-No.</font>
[03/06/2019 00:46:48] <font color="#ffffff">-Espera, espera.</font>
[03/06/2019 00:46:48] <font color="#ffffff">No me digas nada que lo sé.</font>
