[03/06/2019 23:22:21] <font color="#ffff00">adaptarse.</font>
[03/06/2019 23:22:23] <font color="#ffff00">y resolver problemas.</font>
[03/06/2019 23:22:26] <font color="#0000ff">(M SICA)</font>
[03/06/2019 23:22:30] <font color="#ffff00">Pero que un macaco aprenda</font>
